      "SKY HARBOR AIRPORT",
      "Pissy\nX115379\nPOST CARD\nPHOENIX SKY HARBOR\nInternational Airport, Phoenix, Arizona\nAerial view shows the complete Sky Harbor Terminal\nBuilding Complex, built at a cost of over 5 million\ndollars. The fast growing Phoenix area rates in the top\nbracket for total air traffic in the United States.\nDowntown Phoenix can be seen in the distance.\nPhoto by Bob Petley\nDistributed by Petley Studios, 4051 E. Van Buren, Phoenix, Arizona\nPlastichrome®\n205"
